This topic describes how to use Datadog Nozzle for Pivotal Cloud Foundry (PCF).


##<a id="view"></a> View Metrics and Dashboards

1. Review the <a href="https://app.datadoghq.com/screen/integration/cloudfoundry">Cloud Foundry Overview</a> Dashboard in Datadog.

    <%= image_tag("images/cloud-foundry-dashboard.png") %>

1. Explore individual metrics via the <a href="https://app.datadoghq.com/metric/explorer">Metrics explorer</a> page in Datadog, search for metrics beginning with cloudfoundry.nozzle:

    <%= image_tag("images/cf-metrics.png") %>

##<a id="create-alerts"></a> Create Alerts
1. <a href="https://docs.datadoghq.com/guides/monitors/">Create alerts</a> for your Cloud Foundry metrics.

